          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural cerium (isotopic composition: 88.45% 140Ce,",
                "11.11% 142Ce, 0.25% 138Ce and 0.19% 136Ce).",
                "High purity cerium (99.9%) disks of 8 mm diameter and",
                "0.025 mm thickness were cut for preparation of 5",
                "stacked-foil targets. The cutting was performed with",
                "high precision mechanical cutting device. The thickness",
                "of the cerium disks (25+/-3 mu-m) was checked with a",
                " micrometer and also by weighing before and after the",
                "irradiations.",
                "    In each stack target, 4 disks of cerium were used",
                "together with 2 disks of titanium as beam current",
                "monitors. The first titanium monitor was positioned in",
                "front (entrance) of the stack while the second one was",
                "inserted after the second disk of cerium. Additionally,",
                "in order to avoid any losses of activity by recoil",
                "processes, each disk of cerium and titanium was",
                "enveloped by a catcher foil of pure Al of",
                " 22.5 +/- 1 mu-m thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
